reviewText: Recommend this to anyone either in an abusive situation or knowing someone in an abusive situation. Excellent material and resource.

These four segments open people's eyes to the hidden crime of domestic violence, which shockingly occurs even in Christian homes.  Full of important information that would be beneficial to anyone in an abusive relationship and to others who will sooner or later come in contact with people in that situation.  This should be in every church library.
